The Rabbit Hole.name: The Rabbit Hole
The Rabbit Hole.description: Dark tunnel, earthy walls, objects like books and jars suspended mid-air, sense of falling

The Pool of Tears.name: The Pool of Tears
The Pool of Tears.description: Vast pool, shimmering water, floating objects, reflections of a distorted, oversized world

The White Rabbit's House.name: The White Rabbit's House
The White Rabbit's House.description: Victorian-style, small, colorful, quirky decorations, surrounded by a well-kept garden

The Caterpillar's Mushroom.name: The Caterpillar's Mushroom
The Caterpillar's Mushroom.description: Tall, spotted mushroom, lush green forest, misty atmosphere, surreal and oversized

The Duchess's House.name: The Duchess's House
The Duchess's House.description: Chaotic, disheveled exterior, crooked architecture, kitchen visible with clashing utensils

The Mad Tea Party.name: The Mad Tea Party
The Mad Tea Party.description: Long table, mismatched chairs, forest clearing, whimsical tea set, scattered treats and teapots

The Queen's Croquet Ground.name: The Queen's Croquet Ground
The Queen's Croquet Ground.description: Manicured lawn, vibrant rose bushes, some roses being painted red, arches for croquet

The Royal Court.name: The Royal Court
The Royal Court.description: Opulent, open area, diverse crowd of characters, extravagant throne, air of tension and absurdity

The Cheshire Cat's Tree.name: The Cheshire Cat's Tree
The Cheshire Cat's Tree.description: Tall, gnarled tree, tranquil forest area, mysterious aura, branches forming curious shapes

The Lobster Quadrille Beach.name: The Lobster Quadrille Beach
The Lobster Quadrille Beach.description: Sandy beach, calm waters, distant horizon, whimsical sea creatures, serene and inviting
